Description: Wall sherd of East Greek pottery cup or bowl; interior glazed with added red band lined in white; exterior reserved with narrow band on lower wall; inscription in reserved zone.
Findspot: Excavated/Findspot: Sanctuary of Apollo (Naukratis), temenos (said to be)
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GO.204)
